SocialEyez
Please see Job Details for Apply instructions
Saved!
Job Details
READ CAREFULLY & ONLY APPLY IF YOU HAVE SOCIAL MEDIA MARKETING EXPERIENCE:
Social Media Account Manager will lead a team of Account Executives managing one of the largest social media accounts in the UAE. Team is fully responsible for everything to do with content creation, community management, coming up with creative concepts, liaising with creative team, managing campaigns & activations, etc. Account Manager will be in daily communication with management at client side for approvals & regular requests. The candidate must have prior experience managing large social media initiatives. This is an exciting & truly challenging opportunity - requires dedication & experience.
SEND YOUR CV TO info@social-eyez.com
Requirements
Must have minimum 3 years of social media experience Must have excellent written & spoken Arabic & English Must have prior account management experience Will be in charge of one of the largest & most active social media accounts in the UAE
